tafsir[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"ЖҒattanike yimЙ“e Й“en hasboore maЙ“Й“e nden fii golleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Г‘alnde Darngal, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder welsindaare ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e gaayi Laakara on; sabu hilnagol(soklirde) maЙ“Й“e aduna on [wedditoo fii Laakara on]."
  21,2,"Arataa e maЙ“Й“e e Alqur'aana immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e jippiinde kesun, si wanaa Й“e heЙ—ike nde heЙ—agol ngol aldaa e nafa, ko woni, ko heЙ—agol fijindaaru hara Й“e haajaaka ko woni kon e nder mayre."
  21,3,"ЖҒe jenntii mo hari Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko welsindiiЙ—e e makko, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en suuЙ—iri keefeeru ngun yewtere nde Й“e gunndondirta nden e mu'un ko Й“e wi'uЙ“e: ""Enee,taw si oo nodditiiЙ—o wonnde ko o NulaaЙ—o o wonaa si wanaa Й“anndunke yeru mon alaa ko o senndi on e makko?! ko o addi kon ko mbilewu, kaa on jokkay mo hara hiЙ—on anndi ko o Й“anndunke yeru mo'on, Te ko o addi kon kadi ko mbilewu?!"
  21,4,"NulaaЙ—o on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) maaki: ""Joomi am, hiMo Anndi ko suuЙ—uЙ—on kon ka yewtere, ko Kanko woni AnnduЙ—o kala konngol ngol wowloowo wowli ka kammuli e ka leydi, Kanko ko O Nanoowo konnguЙ—i jeyaaЙ“e Й“en, AnnduЙ—o golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, aray O YoЙ“a Й“e e dow Й—um."
  21,5,")Ko woni, Й“e skkki sikkin e fiyaake ko Muhammadu addi kon (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna), tuma goo Й“e wi'a: ""Ko koyЙ—i jillondirЙ—i firo alanaa Й—i"".Tumo goo kadi Й“e wi'a: ""Wanaa non, ko woni, o fefindi Й—i, Й—i maraa lasili"". Tuma goo kadi Й“e wi'a: ""Kanko ko o yimoowo, awa si tawii o laatike goonguЙ—o e nodditagol makko ngol yo o addan men kaawa- seeji, yeru tuggordu Muusaa ndun, e Naaqawa Saalihu mban""."
  21,6,"GomЙ—inaano ado Й“ee weeЙ“ituЙ“e feere, saare toriinde feere fii jippineede Aayeeje Й—en Й“e okkaa nden feere wano Й“e toririinde non, ko woni Й“e fennu Aayeeje Й—en si Men halki Й“e. Mbela Й“eeЙ—oo kadi gomЙ—inay?"
  21,7,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o- si wanaa worЙ“e immorde e Й“anndunke Men wahayina e maЙ“Й“e, Men Nulaali Й“e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e, lanndee tun yimЙ“e defte Й“en ado mo'on si tawii on anndaa Й—um."
  21,8,"Men waЙ—aali NulaaЙ“e, Й“e Men Nuli Й“en joomiraa- Й“e Й“alli Й“e Гұaamataa Гұaametee on, ko woni, hiЙ“e Гұaama wano Гұaamirta tanaa maЙ“Й“e, Й“e wonaali heddotooЙ“e ka aduna hara Й“e maayataa."
  21,9,"Refti Men Goongani NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en ko Men fodi Й“e kon, nokku ka Men danndi Й“e halkeede wonndude e Й“e Men Muuyi Й“en immorde e gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Min halki yawtuЙ“e keerol Й“en sabu yeddugol maЙ“Й“e Alla, e waЙ—Й—itagol maЙ“Й“e geddi Й—in."
  21,10,"GoЙ—ii Men jippinii e mooЙ—on Alqur'aanaare nden no e mayre teddungal mo'on ngal e wasu mo'on ngun si on gomЙ—inii nde, on gollirii ko woni kon e mayre. Kaa on alaa hakkilannde Й—um, sakko yaccoЙ—on faade e gomЙ—inngol nde, e gollirngol ko woni kon e nder mayre?!"
  21,11,"Kaawee ko heewiri wa ca'e Й—e Men halki Й—um sabu tooГұirgol majje keefeeru ngun, Men Tagi Й“aawo majje yimЙ“e goo!"
  21,12,"Tuma nde halkanooЙ“e Й“en yi'unoo Lepte mulayЙ—e Й—en, tawi kamЙ“e hiЙ“e yaccoo doga saare maЙ“Й“e nden immorde e [kulol] halkeede."
  21,13,"ЖҒe noddiroyee fii jalnorgol: ""Wata on dogu dey, yiltee(nduttee) faade e ko wonunoЙ—on e mu'un kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji mo'on, e koЙ—anЙ—e mo'on kadi; belajo'o on lannditoyte goЙ—Й—u e fii aduna mo'on on""."
  21,14,"ЖҒee tooГұooЙ“e qirritoyoo bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in Й“e wi'a: ""Eeyoo, halakuyee amen e hayrere amen, pellet, menen men woniino tooГұuЙ“e sabu yeddugol amen Alla""."
  21,15,"Seerataa qirritagol maЙ“Й“e bakkatuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in e noddugol maЙ“Й“e e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in halakuyee, noddaandu maЙ“Й“e ndu Й“e fillitotoo ndun haa Men waЙ—a Й“e yeru remuru soГұaandu, ko Й“e maayuЙ“e dillugol alanaa Й“e."
  21,16,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji fijindaaru e puyndan, ko woni, Men tagiriiЙ—i fii tinndinorЙ—i e KattanЙ—e Amen."
  21,17,"Sinndo Men faalano jogitaade sonnaajo maaЙ—um Й“iЙ—Й—o Men jogitotono Й—um ko woni kon ka Amen, Men wonaali non waЙ—ooЙ“e Й—um sabu Senagol Amen e Й—um."
  21,18,"Ko woni MeЙ—en werloo Goonga ka Men wahayini kan faade e NulaaЙ“e Amen Й“en e dow meere yimЙ“e geddi Й“en ka fuyna nde, tawa meere maЙ“Й“e nden ko yahunde iwi fes, no woodani on -onon wi'uЙ“e Й“en hiMo jogitii sonnaajo e Й“iЙ—Й—o- halkaare sabu ko sifiЙ—on Mo kon ko O hanndaa e mu'un."
  21,19,"Ko Kanko Tun woodani O Senike laamu kammuu- li Й—in e Laamu leydi ndin, Й“en womЙ“e ka Makko kadi immorde e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en Й“e mawnikin- taaka Dewal Makko ngal, Й“e tampirtaa ngal."
  21,20,"HiЙ“e duumii e Subhinanagol Alla e duumaade, Й“e haaЙ“ataa e Й—um."
  21,21,"Ko woni, sirkooЙ“e Й“en jogiti reweteeЙ—i gaanin Alla, Й—i wuurtintaa mayЙ“e Й“en, ko honno Й“e rewirta ronkuЙ—o gaayi Й—um?!"
  21,22,"Si tawiino laatino ka kammuuli e ka leydi reweteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i Й—i Й—iЙ—i-kala Й—i bonirayno pooЙ—ondiral reweteeЙ“e Й“en ka laamu, ko selli kon no lunndii Й—um, Alla Jom Arsi kin O Senike gaayi ko sirkoЙ“e Й“en sifotoo Mo kon fenaande wonndema no woodani Mo kafidaaЙ“e."
  21,23,"Alla ko Kanko woni teelЙ—o e Laamu Makko ngun e Г‘aawoore Makko nden, hay e gooto lanndotaako Mo fii ko O hoddir kon e ko O Г‘aawi kon, Kanko le O lanndoyto jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en gaayi golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, O yoЙ“a Й“e e dow Й—um."
  21,24,"Ko woni, Й“e jogiti gaanin Alla reweteeЙ—i, maakan an NulaaЙ—o- Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: ""Addee hujja mon on e hanndugol rewugol Й—i, awa ndee Deftere jippinaa- nde e am, e Defte jippinaaЙ—e Й—en e NulaaЙ“e Й“en on maraa hujja e nder majje, ko woni, Й“urЙ“e Й“en e sirkooЙ“e Й“en Й“e tuugutaako si wanaa e majjere e Гұemmbugol, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e e jaЙ“ugol Goonga kan."
  21,25,"Men Nulaali ado maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o- NulaaЙ—o woo si wanaa Men wahayinii e makko pellet, reweteeЙ—o alaa e Goonga si wanaa Miin Rewee Lam Min Tun, wata on kafidu(renndinee) e Am hay e huunde."
  21,26,"SirkooЙ“e Й“en wi'i: ""Alla jogitike Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en Й“iЙ—Й“e rewЙ“e."" O Senike O LaaЙ“ii e Й—en penaali Й—e Й“e wowlata Mo, ko Й“e TeddinaaЙ“e ka Makko, ko woni, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en ko JeyaaЙ“e Alla, TeddinaaЙ“e ka Makko ЖҒattinaaЙ“e e Makko."
  21,27,"ЖҒe adortaa Joomi maЙ“Й“e konngol, Й“e wowlataa Й—um haa O Yamira Й“e, kamЙ“e ko Yamiroore Makko nden Й“e gollata, Й“e lunndantaako Mo Yamiroore."
  21,28,"HiMo Anndi ko yawti kon e ko aroyta kon e golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e torotaako tefoore nden si wanaa e sakkitoore mo O welnaa tefoore mu'un, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e reenii immorde e kulol Makko O Senike, Й“e lunndotaako Mo e Yamiroore wanaa kadi haЙ—oore."
  21,29,"Kala wi'uЙ—o immorde e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en e noone hottagol: ""Min ko mi reweteeЙ—o gaanin Alla"". Menen Men YoЙ“iray mo konngol makko ngol lepte Jahannama Г‘alnde Darngal ko o luttinteeЙ—o e majje, ko yeru ndii njoЙ“di Men yoЙ“ata tooГұirЙ“e Й“en keefaraagal e sirkanngol Alla."
  21,30,"Kaa Й“en yeddu Й“e Alla anndaali woni; wonndema kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin woniino notondirЙ—i, hari heneere alaa hakkunde majji sakko toЙ“o jippoo e mayre, Men senndi hakkunde majji, Men waЙ—i ka ndiyam iwuЙ—aam ka kammu saaЖҙi ka leydi kala huunde immorde e muumi maaЙ—un puЙ—i. Kaa Й“ee taskotaako Й—um, Й“e gomЙ—ina Alla Kanko Tun?!"
  21,31,"Men Tagi ka leydi pelle tabituЙ—e fii wata ndi dimbodu e ko woni kon hoore mayri, Men waЙ—i e mayri laawi yaajuЙ—i belajo'o kamЙ“e Й“e feeway ka jahe maЙ“Й“e faade e faandaaje maЙ“Й“e."
  21,32,"Men waЙ—i kammu ngun kippude reenaandi immorde yanugol ko aldaa e tugaale, e reenaangu immorde e wujjugol nanЙ—e, sirkirooЙ“e Й“en ko woni kon ka kammu immorde e Aayeeje -wano naange ngen e lewru ndun- ko Й—urniiЙ“e Й“e taskotaako."
  21,33,"Alla Kanko Tun woni TaguЙ—o jemma on fii ka fowtee, O Tagi Гұalal ngal ka ngurdan faggitee, O Tagi naange ngen maande fii Гұalorma on, lewru ndun kadi maande fii jemma on, kala majji immorde e naange ngen e lewru ndun hiЙ—i doga e yiilornde majji heeraniinde Й—i, Й—i selataa nde Й—i ooГұataako."
  21,34,"Men waЙ—anaali hay e gooto e Й“anndunke ado maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o- luttineewo e Й—am ngurndam, e hara si lajal maa ngal timmii e Й—a'am ngurndam maayuЙ—aa, hara ko kamЙ“e woni heddotoo Й“e Й“en Й“aawo maaЙ—a? Й—un waЙ—ataa."
  21,35,"Kala wonkii, woni ko gomЙ—inki maa ko yedduki ki meeЙ—ay mayde nden ka aduna, Men jarriboo on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- ka ngurndan aduna e to'e e neema e tampere, refti Й“aawo mayde mon nden ko ka Amen wanaa ka tanaa Amen rutteteЙ—on."
  21,36,"Si yi'ii ma -an NulaaЙ—o- Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, Й“e jogitortaa ma si wanaa jalkitde hiЙ“e raЙ—ora jokkuЙ“e Й“e Й“en wi'igol maЙ“Й“e: ""Enee, ko oo woni yennude reweteeЙ—i mo'on Й—i wonЙ—on rewude Й—in?!"" Hara Й“e jalnorte woni, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e ko Alla jippini kon e maЙ“Й“e immorde ka Alqur'aanaare e ko O okki Й“e kon e neemaaji ko Й“e yeddu Й“e; ko kamЙ“e hanndi e ayiibe on sabu hawtindirgol maЙ“Й“e kala bone."
  21,37,"NeЙ—Й—o on Tagaama e heГұaare, kanko himo heГұora piiji Й—in ado waЙ—ugol majji, ko sabu Й—um si sirkooЙ“e Й“en no heГұara Lepte Й—en, aray Mi holla on -onon heГұorЙ“e Й“en Lepte Am Й—en- ko heГұornoЙ—on kon e Й—um, wata on Й—aЙ“Й“u yaccinaneede Й—um."
  21,38,"HeeferЙ“e yedduЙ“e Immital Й“en hiЙ“e wi'ude e noone heГұorgol: ""Ko honnde tuma ko foduЙ—on men kon laatotoo -ko onon yo JulЙ“e- immorde e Immital si tawii ko on goonguЙ“e e kon ko nodditiЙ—on waЙ—ugol mum."
  21,39,"Sinndo Й“ee heeferЙ“e yedduЙ“e Immital annduno tuma tawi Й“e ruttataa Yiite ngen gaayi geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en wanaa gaayi Й“abbe maЙ“Й“e Й—en kdai, wonnde kadi walloowo alaa mo no walla Й“e duГұugol Lepte Й—en gaayi maЙ“Й“e, sinndo Й“e yananano Й—um Й“e heГұortaano Lepte Й—en."
  21,40,"Ngee Yiite nge Й“e leptetee e mu'un nge arataa e maЙ“Й“e e anndal maЙ“Й“e, ko woni, nge aray e maЙ“Й“e e juhayee, hara Й“e hattantaake yiltugol nge e maЙ“Й“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni nennanoyteeЙ“e haa Й“e tuuba Hinnayee on hewta Й“e."
  21,41,"Si tawii yimЙ“e maaЙ—a Й“en jalkitii ma, haray wanaa an Й—um fuЙ—Й—ori, gomЙ—ii jalkitanoo ma NulaaЙ“e ado maaЙ—a -an NulaaЙ—o- O huЙ“indii yedduЙ“e Й“en, Й“en laatinooЙ“e no jalkita Й“e Lepte Й—en Й“en laatinooЙ“e no jalnora Й“e ka aduna tuma nde NulaaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en hulЙ“inirta Й“e."
  21,42,"Maakan -an NulaaЙ—o- Й“ee heГұorayЙ“e Lepte: ""Ko hommbo reenata on jemma e Гұalorma e kon ko Hinnorante On muuyani on immorde e jippinngol Lepte Й—en e halkugol on?"" ko woni, kamЙ“e gaayi jaЕӢtaade waajuuji Joomi maЙ“Й“e Й—in e hujjaaji Makko Й—in ko Й“e Й—urniiЙ“e, Й“e taskotaako hay e huunde e Й—um sabu majjere e njofoyaagal."
  21,43,"Kaa no woodani Й“e reweteeЙ“e Й“e no dannda Й“e Lepte Amen Й—en? ЖҒe hattantaake wallirde wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in martinngol lorra e majji, Й“e anndantaa Й—i nafa, mo wallaali wonkii mun ko honno o wallirta tanaa makko?! wanaa kamЙ“e kadi woni walloyteeЙ“e immorde e Lepte Amen Й—en."
  21,44,"Ko woni Men dakmitii Й“ee yedduЙ“e, Men dakmitiri baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en sabu ko Men weeЙ“itani Й“e immorde e neemaaji Amen; ka Й—aynugol Й“e, haa jamaanu ngun juutani Й“e, Й“e hoditori Й—um, Й“e ГұiiЙ“i e geddi maЙ“Й“e. Kaa hara Й“ee hoditorЙ“e neemaaji Amen heГұorЙ“e Lepte Amen yi'aali wonnde Menen MeЙ—en ara e leydi ndin Men uytira ndi e bannЕӢeeji mayri doolnugol Amen yimЙ“e mayri, e Polgal Amen e hoore maЙ“Й“e, sakko Й“e taskoo Й—um fii wata yanu e maЙ“Й“e ko yani kon e tanaa maЙ“Й“e?! ЖҒee laataaki fooluЙ“e, ko woni, kamЙ“e ko Й“e foolaaЙ“e."
  21,45,"Maaku -an NulaaЙ—o-: ""Anndu ko mi hulЙ“inirta on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- immorde eLepte Alla ko Wahayu mo Joomi am Wahyini e Am on, faaЙ—uЙ—o on nana- taa Goonga ka Й“e noddaa kan e mu'un nanЙ—e jaЙ“ugol si Й“e hulЙ“iniraama Lepte Alla Й—en."
  21,46,"Mi woondii si meemii Й“ee Й—aЙ“Й“ayЙ“e yaccinaneede Lepte Й—en geЙ“al immorde e Lepte Joomi maaЙ—a Й—en -an NulaaЙ—o- ma Й“e wi'u ontuma: ""Eeyoo, halakuyee amen e hayrere amen, menen men laatike tooГұirЙ“e sirkanngol Alla e fennugol ko Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) Addi kon ""."
  21,47,"Men darna ManndikirЙ—e nunЙ—uЙ—e Й—en fii yimЙ“e Darngal ngal fii yo Й—e manndikire golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, tooГұirtaake e nder nden Г‘alaande hay wonkii uytaneede moЖҙЖҙi makko Й—in maaЙ—um Й“eydaneede bonЙ—e makki, hay si laatike ko peesirgal ngal no famЙ—iri wa yeru ko abbere khardal manndike Й—um Men adday Й—um, Men yonii hasbooЙ“e MeЙ—en hasba golle jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en."
  21,48,"GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo Й“e his) Tawreetaare senndaynde hakkunde Goonga kan e meere nden e hakkunde ko dagii e ko harmi, ko nde Peewal wonannde Й“en gomЙ—inЙ“e nde, ko nde waaju wonannde hulooЙ“e Й“en Joomi mu'un."
  21,49,"ЖҒen hulayЙ“e Lepte Joomi maЙ“Й“e On mo Й“e gomЙ—ini Й—um fii kala Й“e yi'aali mo, hara kamЙ“e hiЙ“e huli Darngal ngal."
  21,50,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare Jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) ko nde waaju wonannde on faalaaЙ—o waajitornde nde heewunde nafa e moЖҙЖҙere. Kaa hara onon on yedday nde wonndude Й—um? Hara on qirritaaki ko woni kon e mayre on gollirtaa nde?"
  21,51,"GomЙ—ii Men Okkii Ibraahiima Hujja e dow yimЙ“e makko Й“en ila ka cukaaku makko hari Men woniino kadi AnnduЙ“e mo, Men Okki mo ko o hanndi kon e mu'un e Ganndal Amen immorde e Hujja e dow yimЙ“e makko Й“en."
  21,52,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko Aajara e yimЙ“e makko Й“en: ""Ko honЙ—um woni Й—ii sanamuuji Й—i moЖҙЖҙinirЙ—on juuЙ—e mon Й—en, ГұiiЙ“uЙ—on e rewgol Й—i?"""
  21,53,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani mo: ""Men tawii baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en no rewaЙ—i, men rewiriЙ—i Гұemmbugol Й“e""."
  21,54,"Ibraahiima Maakani Й“e: ""GomЙ—ii on wonii -onon jokkuЙ“e Й“en- e baabiraaЙ“e mo'on sincuЙ“e Й“en e nder majjere Й“anngunde gaayi Laawol Goongo ngol."
  21,55,"YimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'ani mo: ""Enee, ko soobee addaЙ—aa men, fewndo wowluЙ—aa ko wowluЙ—aa kon, kaa an ko e fijooЙ“e Й“en jeyaЙ—aa?"""
  21,56,"Ibraahiima maaki: ""Ko woni, ko soobee mi addani on wanaa samakala, Joomi mooЙ—on ko Kanko woni Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin On TaguЙ—o Й—i ko aldaa e misal adiingal, min wonndema pellet, Joomi mo'on e Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin miЙ—o jeyaa e seediiЙ“e Й“en, laatanaaki sanamuuji mo'on Й—in geЙ“al immorde e Й—um."
  21,57,"Ibraahiima maaki nokku ka yimЙ“e makko Й“en nanataa: ""Mi woondii, bee tun mi fewja fii Й—ii sanamuuji mo'on ko mettatata on Й“aawo yahugol mon ka juldeere mo'on accaЙ—i."
  21,58,"Ibraahiima munci sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in haa Й—i wonti kuntoy tosokoy, o acci mawndu majji jorto nde Й“e yiltitotoo e mayru fii yo Й“e lanndo ndu ko hommbo munci Й—i."
  21,59,"Tuma nde Й“e ruttinoo Й“e tawi sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in muncaama, yoga e maЙ“Й“e lanndii yoga: ""Ko hommbo munci reweteeЙ—i me'en Й—in? Pellet, on muncuЙ—o Й—i ko e tooГұooЙ“e Й“en o jeyaa, nokku ka o hoyni Й—on ko haani mawninnde e laЙ“Й“innde kon""."
  21,60,"Yoga maЙ“Й“e wi'i: ""Men naniino suka no wowlaЙ—i ko boni himo aybina Й—i himo wi'ee Ibraahiima, no gasa hara ko kanko munci Й—i""."
  21,61,"KoohooЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'i: ""Addee Ibraahiima yeeso yimЙ“e Й“en Й“e yi'a mo; belajo'o Й“e seedoto himo qirritoo ko o huuwi kon, qirritagol makko ngol laatanoo on hujja e hoore makko""."
  21,62,"ЖҒe addi Ibraahiima (yo o his) Й“e lanndii mo: ""Enee, Ibraahiima ko an golle Й—ee golle kaanuЙ—e e sanamuuji amen Й—in?""!"
  21,63,"Ibraahiima maaki -ko o jalnoroowo Й“e, ko o fenГұinЙ—o ronkugol sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in yeeso yimЙ“e Й“en-: ""Mi waЙ—aali Й—um, ko woni, gollii Й—um mawndu sanamuuji Й—in, lanndee sanamuuji mo'on Й—in si Й—i laatike hiЙ—i wowla""."
  21,64,"ЖҒe ruttori e wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in miijitagol e teskagol Й“anngani Й“e wonnde sanamuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—in, Й—i nafataa Й—i lorrataa, ko kamЙ“e woni tooГұuЙ“e fewndo Й“e rewunooЙ—i gaanin Alla."
  21,65,"Refti Й“e ruttii e sanndalЙ—aaku e geddi, Й“e wi'i: ""GomЙ—ii hiЙ—a yananaa -an Ibraahiima- pellet, Й—ii sanamuuji Й—i wowlataa, ko honno yamirirtaa men yo men lanndo Й—i?"" ЖҒe faandori Й—um hujja maЙ“Й“e on, Й—um wonti hujja e hoore maЙ“Й“e."
  21,66,"Ibraahiima maaki -ka mettinanngol Й“e-: ""Enee, on reway gaanin Alla sanamuuji Й—i nafataa on hay e huunde Й—i lorrataa on hay e huunde, kannji ko Й—i ronkuЙ—i e riiwgol lorra kan gaayi ko'e majji, maaЙ—um pooЙ—ugol nafa kan fii majji."
  21,67,"On kaanii, ko rewoton kon kadi ko woori Alla kaanii, Й—ii sanamuuji Й—i nafataa Й—i lorrataa kadi, enee, on hakkiltaa Й—um, Й—alon rewugol Й—i?!"
  21,68,"Tuma nde Й“e ronkunoo tiindorde mo dalil Й“e wallitori doole Й—en, Й“e wi'i: ""Sunniree Ibraahiima yiite ngen; wallee sanamuuji mo'on Й—i o fusi o munci Й—in si tawii on wonii waЙ—ayЙ“e Й—um lepte haЙ—ooje""."
  21,69,"ЖҒe huЙ“Й“ini yiite Й“e werlii mo e magge, Men Daali: ""ko an yo yiite, wonu Й“uuЙ“ol e kisiyee e dow Ibraahiima, nge woniri non, o heЙ“aali lorra""."
  21,70,"YimЙ“e Ibraahiima (yo o his) Й“en faandanii mo pewje fii sunnugol mo, Men bonni pewje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Men waЙ—i Й“e kamЙ“e halkaaЙ“e foolaa."
  21,71,"Men ndanndi mo Men ndanndi kadi Luutu, Men yaltini Й“e, Й“e yahi ka leydi Saami ndin ndi Men barkiniri e mu'un; Nulugol AnnabaaЙ“e e mayri, e sabu ko Men saakani kon tageefooji Й—in e nder mayri immorde e moЖҙЖҙereeji."
  21,72,"Men Okki mo Ishaaqa fewndo o torinoo Joomi makko yo O arsiku mo Й“iЙ—Й—o, Men Okki mo Yaaquuba ka Й“eydugol, gooto-kala immorde e Ibraahiima e geЙ—aljo makko on Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba Men waЙ—i Й“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й—oftiiЙ“e Alla."
  21,73,"Men waЙ—i Й“e AlmaamiiЙ“e, yimЙ“e Й“en no feewira sabu maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere nden, hiЙ“e nodda yimЙ“e Й“en faade e dewal Alla Kanko tun e duЕӢayee Makko O Toowii, Men wahayini e maЙ“Й“e gollee moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, tottiron Julde nden e noone Й“urЙ—o timmude, Itton Jakka on, wonon Й—oftiiЙ“e Men."
  21,74,"E Luutu Men Okki mo serndugol Гұaawoore nden hakkunde wennjiiЙ“e Й“en, Men Okki mo kadi Ganndal e fiyaake Diina makko, Men Hisini mo kadi immorde e lepte Й—i Men jippini Й—en e dow saare makko nden (Saduuma) nde yimЙ“e mu'un laatinoo no huuwa boneeji Й—in, pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bonЙ“e yaltuЙ“e e Й—oftaare Joomi maЙ“Й“e."
  21,75,"Men naadi mo e nder Yurmeende Amen tuma nde Men danndunoo mo immorde e Й—en lepte heЙ“unooЙ—e yimЙ“e makko, pellet, kanko ko o jeyaaЙ—o e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e Й“en, Й“en yamitorayЙ“e Yamiroore Amen, Й“e haЙ—itora kadi haЙ—oore Amen nden."
  21,76,"JaЕӢto kadi -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Nuuhu; tuma nde o noddunoo Alla ko adii Ibraahiima e Luutu, Men jaabinirani mo okkugol mo ko o Й—aЙ“Й“i kon, Men ndanndi yimЙ“e makko gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en immorde e suno mawngo ngon."
  21,77,"Men ndanndi mo e hoЙ—o Й“en yimЙ“e fennuЙ“e ko Men Semmbiniri mo kon immorde e Aayeeje tinndinЙ—e Й—en e goongugol makko. Pellet, kamЙ“e Й“e laatinoke yimЙ“e bone e lorra, Men halkiri Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e yooleede."
  21,78,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Daawuuda e geЙ—aljo makko on Sulaymaana (yo Й“e his) tuma nde Гұaawaynoo e muraadu addaandu ka maЙ“Й“e e fiyaake wennjiiЙ“e Й—iЙ—o; no woodani goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e dammi Й—i saakii jemma e nder ngesa oya mban Й—i bonni mba, Men woni SeediiЙ“e Гұaawoore Daawuuda e Sulaymaana nden, wirnaaki e Amen immorde e Гұaawoore maЙ“Й“e nden hay e huunde."
  21,79,"Men Faamini Sulaymaana Гұaawoore nden gaanin baaba makko Daawuuda, Й“e fow, immorde e Daawuuda e Sulaymaana Men Okki mo Annabaaku ngun e Ganndal fii Гұaawoje Sari'a Й—en, Men hertinanaali Й—um Sulaymaana kanko tun, Men elti wonndude e Daawuuda pelle Й—en hiЙ—e subuhinora subuhinaali makko Й—in, Men eltani mo kadi colli Й—in, Men woni huuwooЙ“e ngol faaminngol e okkugol ГұeeГұal e ganndal e eltugol."
  21,80,"Men Anndini Daawuuda gaanin Sulaymaana tafogol mekeГұaaji (dollokaaji njanndi) fii yo Й—i hiwu on e hewtugol jogaaji Й—in ka Й“alli mo'on. Enee, onon -Й“ee yimЙ“e- on jarnay oo neema mo Alla neeminiri on Й—um."
  21,81,"Men eltani Sulaymaana henndu ndun ko ndu saЙ—tundu wifugol hindu doga e yamiroore makko tuma nde o yamiri ndu faade ka leydi Saami ndi Men barkiniri e mu'un sabu ko Men Nuli kon e mayri immorde e AnnabaaЙ“e, e moЖҙЖҙi weftaaЙ—i e mayri, Men laatike kala huunde ko Men annduЙ“e, hay e huunde suuЙ—otaako Men e Й—um."
  21,82,"Men elti immorde e Seytanuuji Й—in, Й—in Й—i no mutana mo ka maaje Й—i yaltina lu'ulu'uuje e tanaa mu'un, hiЙ—i golla kadi ko wonaa Й—um immorde e golle wano mahugol, Men laatike ko Men ReenuЙ“e limoore majji e golle majji, hay e huunde e Й—um fuutataako Men."
  21,83,"JaЕӢtii -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Ayyuuba (yo o his), tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko O Senike tuma nde jarrabuyee on heЙ“unoo mo ko o wi'uЙ—o: ""Ko an yo Jooma, min dey mi hennaama Гұaw e waaseede Й“eynguure nden, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o Yurmeende yurmeteeЙ“e Й“en fow, martin e am Й—um ko heЙ“i lam""."
  21,84,"Men jaabi toraare makko nden, Men ittini mo ko heЙ“i mo kon immorde e lorra, Men okkiti mo ko o hattinoo kon immorde e Й“eynguure makko e geЙ—al Й“e makko, Men okkiti mo wano maЙ“Й“e wonndude e maЙ“Й“e, kala Й—um Men waЙ—irii Й—um Yurmeende immorde ka Amen, e waaju wonannde kala Й—oftorЙ—o Alla dewal; fii yo o munГұor wano Ayyuuba munГұornoo non."
  21,85,"JaЕӢtii -an NulaaЙ—o- Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli (yo Й“e his), gooto-kala e maЙ“Й“e ko e munГұiiЙ“e jarrabuyee Й“en Й“e jeyaa, e hoore daranagol kon ko Alla fawi Й“e."
  21,86,"Men naadi Й“e e nder Yurmeende Amen, Men waЙ—i Й“e AnnabaaЙ“e, Men naadi Й“e ka Aljanna, pellet, kamЙ“e ko Й“e jeyaaЙ“e e jeyaaЙ“e Alla moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e gollirЙ“e Й“en Й—oftaare Joomi maЙ“Й“e nden, tawi gunndooji maЙ“Й“e e kene maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙi."
  21,87,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii jom linngii ngil Yuunusa (yo o his), tum nde o yahunoo ko aldaa e duЕӢayee(sakkitgol immorde ka Joomi makko ko o tikkanЙ—o yimЙ“e makko Й“en sabu duumagol maЙ“Й“e e geddi Й—in, o sikki wonnde Menen Men Й“ittinan-taa mo; leptirgol fii ko o yahi kon, o jarriboraa saЙ—tude Й“itteede e dummbeede fewndo linngil ngil moЙ—unoo mo, o noddi ka nder niЙ“e reedu linngil ngil e maayo ngon e jemma on; ko o qirritiiЙ—o bakkaatu makko on tuubuЙ—o ka Alla immorde e Й—um, o wi'i: ""ReweteeЙ—o e goonga alaa tanaa MaaЙ—a, A Senike A LaaЙ“ii, min dey mi wonii jeyaaЙ—o e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en""."
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndiri mo immorde e saЙ—teende suno ngon yaltinngol mo ka nder niЙ“e, e ka nder reedu linngil ngil, ko yeru no Yuunusa danndiranoo nii e ndee saЙ—teende makko Й—oo Men danndirta gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en si Й“e yanii e saЙ—teende Й“e torike Alla."
  21,89,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee Jakariyaa (yo o his) tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko Senayee wonanii Mo o maaki: ""Jooma, wata A accan ko mi teelЙ—o hara mi alaa Й“iЙ—Й—o, ko An woni ЖҒurЙ—o MoЖҙЖҙude heddotooЙ“e Й“en, arsikam Й“iЙ—Й—o mo no heddoo Й“aawo am""."
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo toraare makko nden, Men Okki mo Yahyaa Й“iЙ—Й—o, Men moЖҙЖҙini sonnaajo makko on, o wonti jibinoowo Й“aawo hari o laatinoke dimaro, pellet, Jakariyaa e sonna makko e geЙ—aljo makko on Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e heГұoo faade e gollugol moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, Й“e laatinoke hiЙ“e nodda Men hara ko Й“e rerЙ—uЙ“e ko woni kon ka Amen immorde mbarjaari ndin, hara ko Й“e huluЙ“e kon ko woni ka Amen immorde e lepte Й—en, Й“e woniino yankinaniiЙ“e Men."
  21,91,"JaЕӢto -an NulaaЙ—o- fillayee fii Mariyama (yo o his) on reenunooЙ—o farju makko on immorde e jeeno, Alla Nuli e makko Jibriila (yo o his), o wutti e makko o sowii Iisaa (yo o his), [Mariyama] e geЙ—aljo makko on Iisaa Й“e laatike Maande e dow BawЙ—e Alla wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, wonndema pellet, hay e huunde ronkintaa Mo nokku ka O Tagi mo ko aldaa e baaba."
  21,92,"Pellet, kaa Diina mo'on -onon yimЙ“e Й“en- ko Diina woota, Й—um le ko Ngootimpaaku ngun ko ngun woni Diina Lismaamu kan, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on, LaЙ“Й“inanee Lam dewal ngal Min tun."
  21,93,"YimЙ“e Й“en seedi, tawi no e maЙ“Й“e wootinЙ—inЙ—o e sirkuЙ—o e geddo e gomЙ—inЙ—o, Й“ee seeduЙ“e Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e ko ka Amen Menen tun Й“e artiroytee Г‘alnde Darngal, Men yoЙ“a Й“e e dow golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  21,94,"Kala e maЙ“Й“e golluЙ—o golle moЖҙЖҙe Й—en hara himo gomЙ—ini Alla e NulaaЙ—o Makko on e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde nden yiddugol alaa fii golle makko moЖҙЖҙe Й—en, ko woni, Alla jarnay mo O sowana mo mbarjaari ndin, o tawoya Й—um ka nder defter golle makko Гұalnde o immintintee, o weltora Й—um."
  21,95,"Gasantaa yimЙ“e saare nde Men halkiri Й—um sabu geddi mayre nde Й“e ruttotoo ka aduna; fii yo Й“e tuubu tuubuubuyee maЙ“Й“e on jaЙ“ee."
  21,96,"ЖҒe ruttotaako poomaa haa si udditoyaama heedo Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ngon, hara kamЙ“e nden Гұalnde e immorde kala ka towti e leydi nden hiЙ“e yalta hara ko Й“e heГұiiЙ“e."
  21,97,"Darngal ngal Й“adorii sabu yaltugol maЙ“Й“e, kulol maggal e caЙ—eele maggal Й—en feeГұi, e jaka yoo gite yedduЙ“e Й“en no udditii sabu saЙ—tude kulol maggal, Й“e wi'i: ""Ee halkeede amen, gomЙ—ii men laatinoke ka aduna e fijindaaru e welsindaare gaayi heblanagol ndee Г‘alaande Mawnde, ko woni men laatinoke tooГұirЙ“e keefeeru e waЙ—Й—itagol geddi Й—in."
  21,98,"Pellet, onon -Й“ee sirkooЙ“e- e kon ko rewoton ko woori Alla immorde e sanamuuji Й—in, e Й“en weltorayЙ“e ko rewoton Й“e kon jeyaaЙ“e ka yimЙ“e e ka jinnaaji on wonoyay kuЙ“Й“ateeri Jahannama, onon e reweteeЙ“e mo'on Й“en on naatoyay e magge."
  21,99,"Sinndo Й“ee rewaaЙ“e laatino reweteeЙ“e e Goonga Й“e naatataano ka Yiite wonndude e Й“en rewunoo- Й“e Й“e, rewuЙ“e woo rewaaЙ“e woo Й“e fow maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e ka nder Yiite, ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“ooЙ“e ton poomaa Й“e yaltataa e nder magge."
  21,100,"No woodani Й“e nder ton -sabu saЙ—tude muuseendiiji ko Й“e hawrondirta kon- foofaango sЙ—tungo, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e ka Yiite Й“e nanataa hitooji Й—in immorde e saЙ—tude kulol Й—enЖҙinayngol ngol heЙ“ungol Й“e."
  21,101,"Tuma nde sirkooЙ“e Й“en wi'unoo: (Pellet, Iisaa e Malaa'ikaaЙ“e rewanooЙ“e Й“en Й“e naatoyay yiite ngen) Alla Daali: ""Pellet, Й“en Й“e Ganndal Alla aditii e fii mu'un wonnde ko Й“e yimЙ“e Malal ngal wano Iisaa (yo o his) ko Й“e woЙ—Й—inteeЙ“e gaayi Yiite ngen."
  21,102,"Yottotaako e nanЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en hito Jahannama, kamЙ“e hiЙ“e e nder ko wonkiiji maЙ“Й“e Й—in wooЙ—aa kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji Й—in ko Й“e ГұiiЙ“uЙ“e, neemaaji maЙ“Й“e Й—in taЖҙataa poomaa."
  21,103,"Kulol mawngol ngol hulЙ“inoytaaЙ“e tuma Yiite ngen rewnetee e dow yimЙ“e magge Й“en, Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en jaЙ“Й“ora Й“e jarnugol hara hiЙ“e wi'a: ""Ko ndee woni Г‘alaande mo'on nde wonanoЙ—on fodeende nden ka aduna, hiЙ—on weltiniree nder ton Й—in neemaaji Й—i hawroton e mu'un""."
  21,104,"Г‘alnde Men sowoyta kammu ngun yeru sowidugol Й—erol e ko ngol wonndi kon e mu'un, Men mooЙ“oya tageefo ngon e mbaadi maЙ“Й“e ndi Й“e taganoo ndin e mu'un ka laawol aranol, Men fodii Й—um fodoore nde lunndagol alaa e mu'un, pellet, Men laatike SiinooЙ“e ko Men fodi kon."
  21,105,"GomЙ—ii Men winndiino ka defte Й—e Men Tillini Й—um e dow NulaaЙ“e Й“en Й“aawo hari Men winndii Й—um ka Allauwal Reenaangal: ""Pellet, leydi ndin ronoyay ndi jeyaaЙ“e Alla moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e gollirooЙ“e Й“en Й—oftaare Makko nden, Й“en le ko Mofte Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) Й—en""."
  21,106,"Pellet, no e nder koo ko Men jippini immorde e waaju ngun Й“anngal wonannde yimЙ“e rewirooЙ“e Joomi mu'un ko O Sar'inani Й“e kon, ko kamЙ“e woni nafitorooЙ“e Й—um."
  21,107,"Men Nuliraali ma -an Muhammadu- NulaaЙ—o si wanaa Yurmeende denndaangal Tageefo ngon; sabu ko siforЙ—aa kon immorde e rerЙ—ugol fii fewnugol yimЙ“e Й“en e danndugol Й“e immorde e Lepte Alla Й—en."
  21,108,"Maaku -an NulaaЙ—o-: ""Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am immorde e Joomi am ko wonndema ReweteeЙ—o mon On e Goonga ko ReweteeЙ—o Gooto, kafidaaЙ—o alanaa Mo ko Kanko woni Alla, Й—oworee gomЙ—inngol Mo, e gollirgol Й—oftaare Makko nden""."
  21,109,"Si Й“ee Й—urnike ko adduЙ—aa kon, maakan Й“e -an NulaaЙ—o-: ""Mi anndinii on wonndema min e mo'on fiyaake on no fota Й“anngude hakkunde am e mo'on, mi wonaali annduЙ—o ko honnde tuma jippintee e mooЙ—on ko Alla fodi kon immorde e Lepte Makko Й—en."
  21,110,"Pellet, Alla no Anndi ko finГұinto immorde e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suuЙ—o ton kon e maggol, hay e huunde suuЙ—anaaki Mo e Й—um, aray O YoЙ“a on e dow Й—um."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa, no gasa hara nennanngol on Lepte Й—en ko ndarndagol on, e Й—aynugol, e dakmitugol on haa dummunne happaaЙ—o e Ganndal Alla; fii yo on duumi e geddi mo'on e majjere mooЙ—on."
  21,112,"NulaaЙ—o Alla on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) maaki ko O noddayЙ—o Jooma: ""Jooma, senndir hakkunde amen e yimЙ“e amen Й“en, Й“en deppitiiЙ“e e geddi Й—in Г‘aawoore Goongaare nden, ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On men wallitorta e dow ko wowloton immorde e geddi e fennugol ngol""."
